# 3d Lennard-Jones liquid
units lj
dimension 3
boundary p p p
atom_style atomic

lattice fcc 0.844
region simbox block 0 20 0 20 0 20
create_box 1 simbox
create_atoms 1 box

mass 1 1.0

pair_style lj/cut 3.0
pair_coeff 1 1 1.0 1.0 3.0

fix 1 all nve

run 10000

unfix 1

region cut cylinder z 10 10 3 EDGE EDGE
delete_atoms porosity cut 0.5 482793
group cylinder region cut
group stationary subtract all cylinder

velocity cylinder create 1.0 87287
fix 1 cylinder nve
fix 2 cylinder addforce 0.0 0.0 0.1
variable g atom gmask(cylinder)

dump 1 cylinder custom 10 dump.lammpstrj id type x y z vx vy vz v_g
thermo 100
run 50000
